-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Forks consulted for cherry-picks
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

The fork-survey analysis (ANALYSIS_OF_ECHELON_AI_LABS_SERVICENOW_MCP_FORKS.md)
identifies commits from the following MIT-licensed forks of
echelon-ai-labs/servicenow-mcp as cherry-pick candidates for future
phases of this project. Each commit cherry-picked into this repo
preserves its original author via git history. As of Phase 1, no code
from these forks has been merged yet:

  - https://github.com/torkian/servicenow-mcp           (90 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/Flowbie/servicenow-mcp          (194 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/nathanolds22/servicenow-mcp       (2 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/ericstarkey/servicenow-mcp        (2 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/chan4lk/servicenow-mcp           (3 + branch, MIT)
  - https://github.com/klapom/servicenow-mcp            (13 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/patricebechard/servicenow-mcp     (4 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/russ430/servicenow-mcp            (4 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/dobromirmontauk/servicenow-mcp    (4 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/haim-nizri/servicenow-mcp         (3 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/clguo-tw/servicenow-mcp           (2 ahead, MIT)
  - https://github.com/natedolor/servicenow-mcp          (1 ahead, MIT)

Open PRs at echelon-ai-labs/servicenow-mcp may also be the eventual
upstream source for some commits — see ANALYSIS_OF_ECHELON_AI_LABS_PRS_AND_ISSUES.md.
